This is the README for WWW::Wikipedia::LangTitles version 0.04.

WWW::Wikipedia::LangTitles is a "module" for the Perl computer programming
language, a library of computer code to install on a computer.  This
document contains four sections:

1. About - what the module does

2. Documentation - how to learn more about the module

3. Installation - how to install this module on a computer

4. Help - what to do if you get stuck

-----------------------------------------------------------------------------

1. ABOUT

WWW::Wikipedia::LangTitles - get interwiki links from Wikipedia.

This module retrieves the Wikipedia interwiki link titles from the web
site wikidata.org. It can be used, for example, to translate a term in
English into other languages, or to get near equivalents.

-----------------------------------------------------------------------------

2. DOCUMENTATION

You can read the documentation for the module online at the following
websites:

    * http://search.cpan.org/perldoc?WWW::Wikipedia::LangTitles
    * http://metacpan.org/release/WWW-Wikipedia-LangTitles

(These links go to the latest version of the module.)

After installing the module, you can read the documentation on your
computer using

    perldoc WWW::Wikipedia::LangTitles

-----------------------------------------------------------------------------

3. INSTALLATION

This module requires Perl version 5.6.1 or later.

To install the module from CPAN, use

    cpan WWW::Wikipedia::LangTitles

If you have the App::cpanminus installer, you may prefer

    cpanm WWW::Wikipedia::LangTitles

To install the module from the source file,
WWW-Wikipedia-LangTitles-0.04.tar.gz, follow this sequence of commands:

    tar xfz WWW-Wikipedia-LangTitles-0.04.tar.gz
    cd WWW-Wikipedia-LangTitles-0.04
    perl Makefile.PL
    make
    make install

If you want to test the module before installing it, use "make test" after
"make" and before "make install".

-----------------------------------------------------------------------------

4. HELP

To get help with the module, you can email the author, Ben Bullock, at
<bkb@cpan.org>. If you think there is a problem in the module, you can
report a bug at 

<https://github.com/benkasminbullock/www-wikipedia-langtitles/issues>,

or if you want to alter the source code of WWW::Wikipedia::LangTitles, try
the public repository on github at 

<https://github.com/benkasminbullock/www-wikipedia-langtitles>. 

